---
title: Roasted Pepper Fajitas with Smoky Refried Beans and Citrus Sour Cream
description: Roasting peppers in the oven gives them a slight char that’s perfect inside fajitas. Paired with homemade refried beans, citrusy sour cream, and fresh cilantro, these fajitas are bound to be a hit.
